f=AI & Agents/meta/custom/fleet-governance/assets/change-proposal-template.md · h1:Fleet Change Proposal <ID: FCP-YYYYMMDD-nn>=**Proposed by:** <agent> **Date:** <YYYY-MM-DD> **Type:** skill-edit new-agent retire-agent model-change threshold-change **Routes to:** board (Governance Gate) Fleet Charter Rail change applies before verdict. · h2:1. What changes=<One paragraph. Name exact artifact(s): file paths, agent names, registry entries.> · h2:2. Why (evidence)=<The observed problem lesson. Cite: gauge scorecard line, incident report, audit finding, post-mortem, operator request. "It seemed better" evidence.> · h2:Exact diff spec=<For skill edits: before/after text changed section. new agents: full proposed shape agent-architecture-standards. "and related cleanups".> · h2:4. Risk=<What break? Which agents consume changed artifact? Confidence flag rule 0.6: formula-verified reasoning-based.> · h2:5. Rollback=<The exact revert action. trivially revertible, say board weighs that.> · h2:Verdict (board fills in)=APPROVED REJECTED AMENDED (attach diff) Date Archived precedent: <ref>